<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM8.2">
<l>māmutta niticoriyu māmukilkāḷ vēṅkaṭattuc</l>
<l>cāmatti ṉiṟaṅkoṇṭa tāṭāḷaṉ vārttaiyeṉṉē</l>
<l>kāmattī yuḷpukuntu katuvappaṭ ṭiṭaikkaṅkul</l>
<l>ēmattōr teṉṟalukkiṅ kilakkāynā ṉiruppēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O great clouds that pour down big pearls [and] gold!</l>
<l>What tidings of the night-hued great Person from Veṅkaṭam?</l>
<l>Will I remain here as a target for the southern breeze in the middle of the night,</l>
<l>Suffering as the fire of lust entered inside and laid hold over [me]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
